  "title": "Jeju Yacht Tour — Route & Highlights | Grande Bleu Catamaran, Seogwipo Jeju (families with kids)",
  "content": "<div style=\"max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;\"><h1 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:2.25rem;color:#0d2645;margin:0 0 1rem;line-height:1.2;font-weight:600;\">Jeju Yacht Tour — Route & Highlights | Grande Bleu Catamaran, Seogwipo Jeju (families with kids)</h1>\n<figure style=\"margin:1rem auto 2.5rem;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/food_0142.png\" alt=\"Grande Bleu yacht detail Jeju\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(13,38,69,0.18);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">Today's Angle</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">This post focuses on <strong>Route & Highlights</strong>. Grande Bleu sails from Daepo Port, Seogwipo, Jeju on a catamaran sailing yacht, with a cruise time of about 1 hour.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">It is written for families with kids, with practical details that help before booking.</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/influencer_0232.png\" alt=\"Guest enjoying Grande Bleu Jeju yacht\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">What You See On The Route</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">The route introduces Jeju's southern coastline from sea level: Wolpyeong Jusangjeolli, Wolpyeong Sea Cave, Elephant Rock, and the Daepo coastline. The basalt columns feel different when viewed from the water, because you see the height, texture, and coastline in one frame.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">This is not a half-day tour. It is a compact one-hour sailing experience that fits easily into a Jeju itinerary.</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/ocean_0133.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu Jeju sunset sailing\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">Ship And Safety</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Grande Bleu operates catamarans, not single-hull boats. Capacity is 91 guests total: Yacht 550 seats 44 and Yacht 620 seats 47. Each sailing includes a licensed captain and engineer onboard.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">For families, older travelers, and anyone worried about motion, the twin-hull structure is one of the clearest reasons to choose this style of boat.</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/yacht_379_food.jpg\" alt=\"Grande Bleu yacht detail Jeju\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/sail_0080.jpg\" alt=\"Jeju sailing yacht and coastline\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">Onboard Inclusions</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Onboard items include draft beer, wine, Jeju tangerine juice, bottled water, snacks, and cup ramen. The experience is not a formal restaurant cruise; it is a relaxed sea-view hour with drinks, light food, photos, and coastal scenery.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">For photos, watch three moments: just after departure, when the yacht approaches the coastline, and when the light changes before returning to port.</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/influencer_0294.jpg\" alt=\"Guest enjoying Grande Bleu Jeju yacht\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">Price And Booking Channels</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Price guide: Luxury Tour adult ₩60,000 / child ₩40,000, promo ₩48,000 / ₩28,000; Sunset Tour adult ₩70,000 / child ₩40,000, promo ₩56,000 / ₩28,000. Final availability, promotions, language support, and refund rules can differ by booking platform.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Reservations are available through Naver, Klook, KKday, and Ctrip/Trip.com partner platforms. Choose the platform that best matches your country, language, payment method, and change/refund needs.</p>\n<figure style=\"margin:2.75rem auto;max-width:720px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jm7397776-byte/grandebleu-photos/main/influencer_0178.jpg\" alt=\"Guest enjoying Grande Bleu Jeju yacht\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(13,38,69,0.14);display:block;\" /></figure>\n<h2 style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#0d2645;margin:3rem 0 1rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;line-height:1.3;font-weight:600;\">Contact</h2>\n<p style=\"line-height:1.85;margin:0 0 1.25em;font-size:1.0625rem;color:#1a1a1a;\">Phone: +82-64-739-7776. Instagram: @gb.jeju. Phone support is mainly Korean, so overseas travelers should check the booking platform page first.</p></div><p style=\"text-align:center;margin:2rem 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.klook.com/en-US/activity/170600-jeju-grandebleu-sunset-yacht-experience/?utm_source=blogger&utm_medium=cta&utm_campaign=jeju_yacht\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#d4a437;color:#fff;padding:1rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">Sail Before Sunset Tonight →</a></p><p style=\"margin-top:2.2rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#777;border-top:1px solid #eee;padding-top:1rem;\"><a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Jeju%20yacht%20tour\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#Jejuyachttour</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/things%20to%20do%20in%20Jeju\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#thingstodoinJeju</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Jeju%20sunset%20cruise\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#Jejusunsetcruise</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Grande%20Bleu\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#GrandeBleu</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Daepo%20Port\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#DaepoPort</a> · <a href=\"https://jejugrandebleuyacht.blogspot.com/search/label/Seogwipo\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:none;\">#Seogwipo</a></p>",
